  <div class="sb_box br-bg">
    <h3 class="right_title">
      <div class="position">当前位置：<a href="/" title="首页">首页</a> &gt; <a href="/about/?2.html">潍博之信</a>&gt; <a href="/list/?3_1.html">规章制度</a></div>
      <span>规章制度</span> </h3>
    <div class="clear"></div>
    <div class="active" id="shownews">
      <h1 class="title">第十七章  值班制度</h1>
      <div class="editor"><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第一条</span> </span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">加强办公楼值班管理，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">更好发挥好</span>“窗口单位”职能作用，营造“扎实严谨、务实高效”的工作氛围</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第二条</span> &nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">值班规定</span></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、值班时间</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">：</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">每周六、周日及节假日（上午</span>8：15—11:45；10月1日—次年4月30日：下午13:30—17:30，5月1日—9月30日：14：00—18：00）</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">二</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、值班人员：办公楼</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">工作人员。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">三、</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">值班地点：二楼微机室外间</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">四、</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">值班实行一人负责制，轮流值班（值班后可再补休）</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">五、</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">值班期间要忠于职守，严禁迟到、早退及无故脱岗现象，个人若遇特殊情况需请假，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">须有人替换，并报知办公室。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">六、</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">电话记录、会议通知、文件材料的</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">接收</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、重要接待任务及其它综合性行政事务的处理要做到及时、准确，电话会议记录要准确、详实（写明会议通知部门、发话人姓名、会议时间、地点、内容、参会人员及注意事项）并及时向主要领导汇报做相应安排，并严禁公话私用，遇有重要接待任务，要及时向主要领导及值班领导汇报，并通知相关人员做好接待准备</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">七</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、要爱护办公设施及办公室原有物品，若有损坏、丢失，将追究当班人员责任，并予以赔偿。</span></span></p><p><br/></p><script src="/inc/AspCms_VisitsAdd.asp?id=463"></script></div>
      
      <div class="met_page">上一条：没有了!&nbsp;&nbsp;下一条：<a href="/content/?464.html">第十六章  网络管理</a></div>
